                                                "headline": "Powerful REST API",
                                                "text": "Pirsch was built from the ground up with automation in mind. Use the REST API to create dashboards, manage permissions, send traffic, and read statistics.<br><br>Fine-grained permission management makes it possible to work with a single dashboard or on an account basis, managing as many sites as you want. Whatever your use case, Pirsch integrates seamlessly into your application.",
